Google Map Scraping & Research (Large Scale)
--------------------------------------
- Search data in google map
- Searching Data (email, phone) From Website
- Searching Data from Facebook
- Searching Data from instagram
- Copy data by using Clip Board
- Paste data from Clip Board to Excel/Google Sheet

Requirement
------------------
Hello, my name is Steve and I am the Head of Sales for a company based in New Zealand. 
I need 500 leads that can be obtained from Google Maps for B2B cold calling. I'm looking 
for a reliable partner with whom I can establish a long-term business relationship. I want 
someone I can consistently order from.

Data I Require:

1.       Company Name		11.   Google Photo count
2.       Company Domain Name	12.   Google Place ID
3.       Phone Number		13.   Google Plus Code
4.       Address		14.   Google Location Link
5.       Postal Code		15.   Google Reviews ID
6.       City			16.   Facebook URL
7.       Country		17.   LinkedIn Page
8.       Industry		18.   Instagram page
9.       Google Rating		19.   Twitter page
10.      Google Reviews		20.   Contact Email address

Before importing the list to my CRM, I need some formatting done to it. I want below specific industries, including these industries initially.

- Air Conditioning
- Heat Pumps in New Zealand
- Tire Shops in New Zealand
- Hire Shops in New Zealand
I want the data for every listing in each industry.


Working Process:
-------------------
Step-1: Prepare a Excel Sheet/Google Sheet below way
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Serial	| Company Name |Domain Name | Phone Number | Contact Email address | Address | Postal Code | City | Country | Industry | Google Rating 	| Google Reviews |  Google Photo count |  Google Place ID | Google Plus Code | Google Location Link | Google Reviews ID | Facebook URL | Facebook URL | LinkedIn Page | Instagram page |  Twitter page 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
	|	       |	                   |	                   |         |             |      |         |          |                |                |                          |                           |                                |                             |                              |                                  |                                |                          |                          |                        |                         |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


Step-2: Find cities list of New Zealand
- Open chrome browser and type "city list of new zealand"
- go to "Wikipedia" and copy city list in note pade

Step-2: Data Collection
- Open chrome browser and type "Heat Pumps in Wellington, New Zealand" and press enter
- click on "Maps" 
- continue scroll down to get more data
- click on a link
- copy data in ClipBoard
- paste data from ClipBoard to Excel Sheet











